      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable daily driver, and I think you\u2019re going to love it! It\u2019s been such a great car for me\u2014always dependable and super smooth on the road. It\u2019s in really nice shape, with just the usual character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s been enjoyed, but it\u2019s still got so many miles of fun left to give. If you're looking for a solid ride that\u2019s ready to go from day one, this is definitely it. I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home, so feel free to message me with any questions!",
