    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine known for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring an engaging, analog driving experience. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a documented rod bearing service and replacement of the throttle actuators. The suspension retains its composure with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing versatile damping profiles, while the carbon fiber roof remains structurally pristine, keeping the center of gravity low. A true driver\u2019s specification with a focus on longitudinal and lateral performance.",
