    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway driving and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery has been regularly conditioned and remains supple, showing only light character lines on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recently installed set of high-performance all-season tires. It delivers a smooth, confident driving experience with crisp gear shifts and responsive braking. This is an honest, well-loved car that has been kept to high standards, offering the next owner a turnkey experience with no immediate service needs.",
